{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"VGLSQgjkL1invoOn1WIVU","title":"Operation Rewrite","desc":"","updated":1645087917572,"created":1644384514239,"custom":{},"fname":"projects.operation-rewrite","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"28580c3472a24101a1666db5b7294ada","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"projects.operation-rewrite","id":"VGLSQgjkL1invoOn1WIVU","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"web.frontend.rendering-strategies","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":5,"offset":660},"end":{"line":28,"column":42,"offset":697},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web.frontend.rendering-strategies"}}],"anchors":{"project-operation-re-write-purposely-obscure":{"type":"header","text":"Project: Operation Re-write (Purposely obscure)","value":"project-operation-re-write-purposely-obscure","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"problem":{"type":"header","text":"Problem:","value":"problem","line":10,"column":0,"depth":3},"solution":{"type":"header","text":"Solution:","value":"solution","line":14,"column":0,"depth":3},"existing-stack":{"type":"header","text":"Existing stack","value":"existing-stack","line":18,"column":0,"depth":3},"proposed-re-architected-stack":{"type":"header","text":"Proposed re-architected stack:","value":"proposed-re-architected-stack","line":25,"column":0,"depth":3},"rendering-style":{"type":"header","text":"Rendering Style","value":"rendering-style","line":32,"column":0,"depth":3},"framework-options":{"type":"header","text":"Framework Options","value":"framework-options","line":42,"column":0,"depth":3},"headless-cms-options":{"type":"header","text":"Headless CMS Options","value":"headless-cms-options","line":48,"column":0,"depth":3},"db":{"type":"header","text":"DB?","value":"db","line":53,"column":0,"depth":3},"build-steps":{"type":"header","text":"Build steps","value":"build-steps","line":59,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"6FtP5bCaxDDd47jEuSH5y","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"operation-rewrite\">Operation Rewrite<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#operation-rewrite\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"project-operation-re-write-purposely-obscure\">Project: Operation Re-write (Purposely obscure)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#project-operation-re-write-purposely-obscure\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"problem\">Problem:<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#problem\"></a></h3>\n<p>Existing site is slow and difficult to improve given it's built in wordpress. Gives limited options for improvement from a developer perspective without adding more bloat and plugins. Owned by non-for-profit therefore budget is an important consideration.</p>\n<h3 id=\"solution\">Solution:<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#solution\"></a></h3>\n<p>Re-write using headless CMS and following JAMSTACK princples.</p>\n<h3 id=\"existing-stack\">Existing stack<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#existing-stack\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Frontend: PHP</li>\n<li>Backend: PHP</li>\n<li>CMS: Wordpress</li>\n<li>DB: SQL</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"proposed-re-architected-stack\">Proposed re-architected stack:<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#proposed-re-architected-stack\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Frontend: React framework</li>\n<li>Backend - possibly NodeJS with GraphQL</li>\n<li>CMS: Headless</li>\n<li>DB: ?? not sure if I need one</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"rendering-style\">Rendering Style<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#rendering-style\"></a></h3>\n<p>Ref <a href=\"/KnowledgeGarden/notes/KnACyiSV918ASnIeSH2TQ\">Rendering Design Patterns / Strategies</a></p>\n<p>Options: SSR, SSG, SPA, ISR</p>\n<p>Content is mostly static - new blog posts written relatively infrequently. There is an ecommerce section with a small number of products. No comments or anything else that is dynamic at the moment.</p>\n<p>SSG could be a good option here but a framework that supports SSR as well could be useful for any future concerns. Maybe best of both worlds and use ISR? No need to rebuild every time we change a post or add a product.</p>\n<h3 id=\"framework-options\">Framework Options<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#framework-options\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Remix - looks good but pretty new</li>\n<li>Next - established, but maybe bloated for my use case? Needs a server to run for ISR and SSR</li>\n<li>Gatsby - only does SSG (?)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"headless-cms-options\">Headless CMS Options<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#headless-cms-options\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Strapi - free/open source</li>\n<li>Contentful - recommended but paid after certain point</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"db\">DB?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#db\"></a></h3>\n<p>Do I need?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>PSQL</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"build-steps\">Build steps<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#build-steps\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Set up CMS</li>\n<li>Set up FE</li>\n<li>interface the two</li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"wn8PE1RhG0znK1alrGFYv","title":"Knowledge Garden","desc":"","updated":1725627729985,"created":1631901573363,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"8d5496c75d3dbc62da1263726aa08b42","links":[],"anchors":{"my-second-brain":{"type":"header","text":"My Second Brain","value":"my-second-brain","line":8,"column":0,"depth":4}},"children":["bwlvrHRccHBUBhHu7Mh1G","7w0mtdy9yip2z8dm44sazxg","8h567033xcainsquqy92vos","514eyidh124uj7yywy9os9z","zbqz5oql3yy88t9yf8q9mtz","XZTCg1c8mZeR9jEyM2HOy","6FtP5bCaxDDd47jEuSH5y","5c0e9ifp2lh9imgp1zahq33","aig5i0xuh2jq0ibzfq8sz22","8HZ1TTh4HUtNFePL29cg7"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n#### My Second Brain\n\n---\n\nA collection of my notes around all things software development.\n\n> This website is generated by a Dend